newest.message:
== Contributors for this version ==
* Jimi
== Enhancements ==
* Prerequisites of an already known skill will no longer be included in the skill plan. * Added identification names to planetary pins. * Implementation of new implants API format and jump clones info. * Added additional API info of the IndustryJobs endpoint.
== Misc ==
* Plan management window now shows in Taskbar. * Several improvements have been done to the base code to make EVEMon a better application.
